item.title: CVE-2023-5415|2023-11-22T15:33:26.588Z -- funnelforms -- interactive%20contact%20form%20and%20multi%20step%20form%20builder%20with%20drag%20%26%20drop%20editor%20%E2%80%93%20funnelforms%20free
item.description: The Funnelforms Free plugin for WordPress is vulnerable to unauthorized modification of data due to a missing capability check on the fnsf_add_category function in versions up to, and including, 3.4. This makes it possible for authenticated attackers, with subscriber-level permissions and above, to add new categories.
